<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA60">
<l>ōruruva ṉallai yoḷiyuruva niṉṉuruva</l>
<l>mīruruva ṉeṉpa rirunilattō – rōruruva</l>
<l>mātiyām vaṇṇa maṟintā ravarkaṇṭīr</l>
<l>nītiyāṉ maṇkāppār niṉṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You do not have a single form; the light form is your form.</l>
<l>‘He has two forms,’ they say, they of the vast land, who have understood</l>
<l>the manner in which in the beginning there was one form. They, see,</l>
<l>constantly guard the earth according to the rule.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
